Name: Romania Foreign Exchange Reserves Millions Of National Currency
Metadata: Source: Eurostat. Eurostat collects data from the statistical agencies of the 27 member countries of the European Economic Community, candidate countries (Macedonia, Croatia and Turkey), EFTA countries (Iceland, Norway, Liechtenstein and Switzerland) as well as other countries (Japan, Australia, United States). Statistical agencies within each country disseminate their national data to Eurostat in order that it can be made available in a consistent format.
